This patch is necessary on,

* Android 16 - yes
* Android 15 - yes
* Android 14 - untested
* Android 13 - untested
* Android 12 - untested
* Android 11 - untested
* Andoird 10 - untested

we might apply it at all proot-distro installations regardles.

